RevisionNumber Property

Requires: Base Development System

Class: VI Properties (ActiveX)

Current revision number of the VI.

When writing this property, you can write only a value greater than the current revision number. If you attempt to write a revision number whose value is less than the current revision number, the property returns an error.

This property is similar to the options available in the Revision History page of the LabVIEW VI Properties dialog box.

Syntax

object.RevisionNumber

Data Type

long
